{
  "stem": "24544.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because I knew he's coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he took me to the ambulance, put cream on me, and put again all the gaze on me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then, he was happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They didn't want anything from me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Just to see me, they gave me a correct treatment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "People hate me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "People hate me for that-- but I was absolutely innocent-- Because I have a special care.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I have a special care.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went back again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took off me the gaze-- the gaze and then treated the other sick people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a torture for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was hated for that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all of the sudden, that yellow officer, who took care of the [NON-ENGLISH]-- I always say [NON-ENGLISH], that bread ration cell, we called cell-- took me in the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But not Lloyd, the insurance company, has insurance better than it was there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Otherwise, that was the most terrible things what ever happened to me, because my mother still was walking out to work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, that is [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Botten, ?] everything, already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm going to sing that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That song which comes was made up by the labor camps people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got it, somehow, on the grapevine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the people was crying and close to the nervous breakdown, was a girl, gypsy girl, we called.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was from East Hungary, so she took-- she could talk with the Ukraines, the guards.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were good friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she stood up the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was sleeping in the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And watching out every night when the people came out-- came in from the work, is my mother returned or not?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the most terrible time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she stood up.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
